.SH NAME
list sheet \- Show only sheet music entries
.SH SYNOPSIS
alexandria> list sheet
.SH DESCRIPTION
Filters the library to items with type \fBSheetMusic\fR.
.br
Useful when you want a clean repertoire-only view.
